original_title: Bronx: Muliner Avenue - Morris Park Avenue
text:
Muliner Avenue (telephone poles thereon), between Morris Park and Rhinelander Avenues, showing two frame houses where Delancey Place comes up to meet them from the south. This view is northeastward from Matthews Avenue. Note Public School No. 83, among the trees.

June 22, 1940

P. L. Sperr
